        "content": "<p>Hope you don't mind me jumping in, but could it be just a missed <code>#whr</code> here? </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"o\">---</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">internal</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">src</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">pin_data</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rs</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+++</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">internal</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">src</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">pin_data</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rs</span>\n<span class=\"o\">@@</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">304</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">7</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"mi\">304</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">9</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">@@</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">generate_projections</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"cp\">#[doc = #docs]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"cp\">#[allow(dead_code)]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"cp\">#[doc(hidden)]</span>\n<span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"n\">vis</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"n\">projection</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"n\">generics_with_pin_lt</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"n\">vis</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"n\">projection</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"n\">generics_with_pin_lt</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"n\">whr</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"p\">#(#</span><span class=\"n\">fields_decl</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">*</span>\n<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"n\">___pin_phantom_data</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">core</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">marker</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">PhantomData</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;&amp;'</span><span class=\"nb\">__</span><span class=\"na\">pin</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
